    or from CVS:

	cvs.fidogate.sourceforge.net

===============================================================================
1.  Compiling and installing

    Before begining compile necessary unpack fidogate
      
	tar xIvf fidogate-X.X.X.tar.bz2
      
or if it packed by gzip:
      
	tar xzvf fidogate-X.X.X.tar.gz
      
    Enter to created directory and run configure script with necessary parameters.
Check validate created configs `config.h' and `build/config.make'.

1.1.	CONFIG.H

1.2.	CONFIG.MAKE

Run "make depend" (здесь и далее имеется в виду GNU make). Далее "make",
"make install", "make install-config".


2.  Файлы конфигурации и их описание.

    У fidogate имеется ряд конфигурационных файлов:

    2.1		acl
    2.2		aliases
    2.3		areas
    2.4		fidogate.conf
    2.5		ftnacl
    2.6		hosts
    2.7		packing
    2.8		passwd
    2.9		routing
    2.10	spyes
    2.11	uplinks
    
    2.12	areas.bbs
    2.13	fareas.bbs
    
    Для связывания с Mail-Transport-Agent (MTA):

    3.1		sendmail:
		    ftn.m4
		    mailertables

    3.2		postfix:
		    master.cf
		    transport
    3.3
		exim:

    3.4
		qmail:

    3.5
		smail:

    For linked with InterNetNews (INN):

    4.1		newsfeeds

    5.1		Description for any programs

<to be contenued>

